## Naming Conventions

| What | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| React components | PascalCase | `PlanCard.tsx`, `GateMarker.tsx` |
| Hooks | camelCase prefixed `use` | `usePlan.ts`, `usePhases.ts` |
| Server Actions files | camelCase | `actions/plans.ts` |
| Utility functions | camelCase | `formatProgress`, `getGateStatus` |
| Types & Interfaces | PascalCase, no `I` prefix | `Plan`, `Phase`, `Block`, `Gate` |
| Route files | lowercase, App Router convention | `page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, `route.ts` |
| CSS Modules | camelCase | `styles.module.css` → `styles.container` |
| Supabase table refs | snake_case (matches DB) | `training_plans`, `phases` |

